long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Nursery Downloader makes it easy to download your nursery photos in bulk.

The extension downloads all of your photos directly to your computer, at the click of a button.

This extension currently only works with ParentZone and Famly
